sequenceDiagram
    participant Saler
    participant SalerWeb
    participant Auth as AuthController
    participant UserSvc as UserService
    participant DB
    participant Noti as NotificationService
    Saler->>SalerWeb: Mở trang đăng ký
    Saler->>SalerWeb: Nhập username/email/password + role=Saler
    SalerWeb->>Auth: POST /api/auth/register
    Auth->>UserSvc: ValidateDto(dto)
    UserSvc-->>Auth: Valid
    Auth->>DB: SELECT * FROM Users WHERE Username=? OR Email=?
    DB-->>Auth: None
    Auth->>UserSvc: HashPassword(dto.Password)
    UserSvc-->>Auth: PasswordHash
    Auth->>DB: INSERT User (role=Saler, IsActive=true)
    DB-->>Auth: UserId
    Auth->>Noti: Notify admin "New saler registered"
    Auth-->>SalerWeb: 200 {userId, token}
    SalerWeb-->>Saler: Đăng ký thành công, chuyển sang dashboard
